reviews.text: Excellent premium wagyu beef set.  Beef was fresh and flavourful. Side dishes of salad and kimchi were tasty too. Restaurant has a cosy setting. Ventilation was good and place was not overly filled with BBQ smoke. Good selection of drinks including non-alcoholic, cocktails and beef. Nice finisher of grilled rice-cakes and ice-cream for dessert.
Nice food but bad service
Excellent beef. Too quality wagyu. Need to order special menu.
I had set dinner for two. The platter was generally good but as seen in the photo, the pork was too fat and I could hardly eat it
Lunch quite good

result.name: 燒肉の牛太・本陣

reviews.text: 這次三個人 點了兩份$438套餐，食材新鮮好吃，生菜也好好吃！  雖然我不會講粵語 但是服務人員人都很好，專業又親切，下次有機會再到香港旅行的話 會再去吃的～～ (⁎⁍̴̛ᴗ⁍̴̛⁎)
點了一個$438 套餐外加一份牛肋肉同豆腐鍋，同老婆兩個人食剛剛好，各種肉類都十分新鮮，配上醬油同海鹽味道很好👍🏻店員很專業，服務態度很好同有禮貌，會再度光顧。
服務員態度十分親切，肉的味道很好吃，特別是豬肋骨，超好味！

Excellent premium wagyu beef set.  Beef was fresh and flavourful. Side dishes of salad and kimchi were tasty too. Restaurant has a cosy setting. Ventilation was good and place was not overly filled with BBQ smoke. Good selection of drinks including non-alcoholic, cocktails and beef. Nice finisher of grilled rice-cakes and ice-cream for dessert.

無野食的放題。。。
食左近兩個鐘， 未飽。  追幾次都係等等等。。。
